Fleetwood sliding glass doors lead out to a lovely patio with beautiful ocean views and the grassy area of Palisades Park. The one bedroom has been transformed into a modern open area of kitchen, entertaining area and bedroom. Off the bedroom is a full sized bathroom. The engineered wood floors throughout bring a rich tone to compliment the bright white walls giving a "beachy" vibe. Parking is not a problem as this comes with one spot in the gated garage. The complex has a lovely ground level swimming pool with front desk services during the day. One block away from Wilshire Blvd with fantastic shops, restaurants, entertainment Third Street Promenade and new metro line.

api_list.description: Get a list of properties by providing the zillow search results URL

api_list.name: Search for properties

required_parameters.name: location
required_parameters.description: Location details, address, county, neighborhood or Zip code.

optional_parameters.name: sort
optional_parameters.description:
For `status_type` = `ForSale` OR `RecentlySold` are available:
- `Homes_for_You`
- `Price_High_Low`
- `Price_Low_High`
- `Newest`
- `Bedrooms`
- `Bathrooms`
- `Square_Feet`
- `Lot_Size`

default `Homes_for_You`

For `status_type` = `ForRent` are available:
- `Verified_Source`
- `Payment_High_Low`
- `Payment_Low_High`
- `Newest`
- `Bedrooms`
- `Bathrooms`
- `Square_Feet`
- `Lot_Size`

default `Verified_Source`

optional_parameters.name: home_type
optional_parameters.description:
Property type comma-separated or empty for all types:
- `Multi-family`
- `Apartments`
- `Houses`
- `Manufactured`
- `Condos`
- `LotsLand`
- `Townhomes`

optional_parameters.name: otherListings
optional_parameters.description: If set to 1, the results will only include data from the `Other Listings` tab.

optional_parameters.name: daysOn
optional_parameters.description:
Days on Zillow possible values :
- empty: Any,
- 1: 1 day,
- 7: 7 days,
- 14: 14 days,
- 30: 30 days,
- 90: 90 days,
- 6m: 6 months,
- 12m: 12 months,
- 24m: 24 months,
- 36m: 36 months

optional_parameters.name: page
optional_parameters.description: Page number if at the previous response `totalPages` > 1

optional_parameters.name: status_type
optional_parameters.description:
Status type of the properties

Default : forSale

- forSale

- forRent

- recentlySold
